ed_days):\n    raise ValueError(f\"Missing observed values for days: {[d for d in required_days if d not in observed]}\")\n\nmae = sum(abs(forecast[d] - observed[d]) for d in required_days) / len(required_days)\n\nprint({\n    \"forecast_ap\": [forecast[d] for d in required_days],\n    \"observed_ap\": [observed[d] for d in required_days],\n    \"mae\": mae,\n})", "reason": "Repaired the code to work in the sandbox by fetching the NOAA forecast text files directly from the provided S3-backed public HTTP path instead of a missing local file. It parses the Mar 9, 2025 forecasted Ap values for Mar 10-12 and the observed Ap values from the Mar 11-13 issued files, computes MAE, and prints the result."}) [toolUseId=call_jhuQGbWj4RuDZ603PpOH523s]
